ajor partnership deal with luxury fashion site farfetch“we are excited to welcome abercrombie  fitch to the tmall platform” said jessica liu president of tmall fashion alibaba group “abercrombie is an iconic global brand that consumers both on our platform and in china have sought out for some time we look forward to connecting our consumer base to the brand and working with abercrombie  fitch to further its international growth”this article is about china abercrombie and fitch alibaba tmall advertising marketing media brandshare to twittershare to linkedinshare to facebookget the newsletterkeep up to date with the latest news and insightssubscribeshawn limshawn lim is a reporter at the drum covering industry news around the asia pacific region with a focus on singapore and southeast asia based in singapore he has worked across photography video and online covering a range of subjects including current affairs and sportsbefore game of thrones he was a huge breaking bad fan he does crossfit and yoga to stay healthytwitterall by shawn lets get social follow us on twitterfind us on instagramjoin us on linkedinfind us on facebook related articleschinaabercrombie and fitchalibabatmalladvertisingmarketingmediabrandaudi slammed for advertisement comparing women to used cars in china july alibaba merges online and offline shopping experience with three new physical stores  july jdcoms  shopping festival takes record breaking bn in sales  june abercrombie  fitch eyes opportunity to ‘redefine’ gilly hicks brand as it brings it back to january more must watchvideothe rise of the consultancies accenture ey deloitte and ibm are finding their industry groovevideowelcome to the mind of mark denton a look at the work in his art mart gallery videodisturbing london grows taller than tinie tempah in creative collaboration with mercedes’ smartvideoair france has launched its own inflight chewing gum so the drum put it to the testvideologos lies and monochrome the enduring legacy of woo